{"tid":1433821,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"時間就係得咁多 你想自己話事定黑社會話事？","createTime":"2019-08-08T14:57:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T00:52:54.000Z","uid":75959,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cf7a9269fb202343e8e17122b5b4ada1d64e7bfb","tid":1433821,"uid":75959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:57:23.000Z","msg":"黑社會記招日日都有，但就日日都無新update。人地用呢個記招做文宣，壯聲勢，拉攏中立游離派，加強對垃圾藍絲廢佬的思想洗腦，你地就浪費光陰，好似師奶茶餘飯後笑鳩人。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">好心用下個腦，諗下點解要俾人帶風向討論。時間就係得咁多，要自己主場定黑社會做主場，你自己諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">文宣就一路係到，你地幾時先會send俾非同溫層知<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好浪費勇武巴絲的一片苦心好無？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">不割蓆，不篤非，兄弟爬山，齊上齊落!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"d897e4444da59e6823555e0076c5a708d4d9141a","tid":1433821,"uid":75959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:58:24.000Z","msg":"拒絕做無知豬<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"9e806e914200835181913a718f034d78caca2a38","tid":1433821,"uid":75959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:00:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d3f9161d8f0e29af60cb8347217d661f715ed24","tid":1433821,"uid":4050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:01:02.000Z","msg":"咪係"},{"pid":"afac34f7e888ad7043289bf703ec5653831e7c2e","tid":1433821,"uid":75959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:03:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: